Install kickstarter from https://meego.gitorious.org/meego-developer-tools/kickstarter

NOTE: There are some patches needed to upstream kickstarter to update the .ks files properly
updated kickstarter can be found from https://meego.gitorious.org/~sage/meego-developer-tools/sages-kickstarter
and the MR against upstream kickstarter from https://meego.gitorious.org/meego-developer-tools/kickstarter/merge_requests/4

$ git clone git://gitorious.org/~sage/meego-developer-tools/sages-kickstarter.git
$ cd kickstarter
$ make
$ sudo python ./setup.py

More information can be found from: https://meego.gitorious.org/meego-developer-tools/kickstarter/blobs/master/README

Updating .ks files

$ kickstarter -c configurations.yaml -r repos.yaml
